content.description:
This is a fun, easy, flake climb to a slab top out. From the tree, head up and right to gain the flake. Cruise up the flake until it meets with the crack on the left (

Good Enough For Government

). From there, head up and right past one piece of pro on the slab, then head to the topout. The flake is 5.easy, and the start of the slab is the 5.5 section.
